To run this Backend code and start the server you need to follow somesteps

Step1: Go to the node.js website the download the lastest version of node 
https://nodejs.org/en

Step2: Clone the repo and download the zip file of this project 

Step3: Hit npm i or npm install  to install all dependecies in to your project

Step4: In last hit npm run dev, now you are set and free to access all the api

Note: Use the postman, thunderclient or any other API testing tool or API client.
